SimpleGit Ruby Library
======================

This library calls git commands and returns the output.

TJM - following along with Scott's excellent read Git Internals Peepcode (peepcode-git.pdf)
TJM - another change to test git commit without -m

Recloning Scott's simplegit repositoru
To put Scott's repository into my GitHub
	1. Clone Scott's repository git clone https://github.com/schacon/simplegit.git
	2. Create peepcode-simple repository --> https://github.com/timmac62/peepcode-simple.git
	3. g remote rename origin upstream
	4. g remote add origin https://github.com/timmac62/peepcode-simple.git
	5. g push origin master

Author : Scott Chacon